reviewText: All I can say is, this is very unprofessional and poor quality.  Hard to believe it is packaged and sold on Amazon.  Beware when buying things with no reviews.  This was so bad, it drew the attention of people that were not watching the DVD (we were watching it on the computer).  Just a random person videotaping their self.  Poorly done.  We just shut it off and got on YouTube.  That was much better than this video!  Plan to return it.
This was for a gift and she says she likes it.
